  "description": {
    "zh": "这个挑战可能更容易一些，但仍然是个挑战，毕竟大多数行动人员都避免使用这些。\n这次是为使用7.62x54mm R（俗称\"莫辛纳甘弹药\"）的武器准备的。\n\n指定弹匣：\n - AVT-40 7.62x54R 10发弹匣\n - SVD 7.62x54 10发弹匣",
    "en": "This one might be easier, but still a challenge, after all most operators avoid using these.\nIt's for weapons chambered in 7.62x54mm R, \"mosin nagant ammo\" as some might call it.\n\nSpecified Magazines :\n - SVT-40 7.62x54R 10-Round Magazine\n - SVD 7.62x54R 10-Round Magazine"
  },
